 } } \right]$$<br><br>$$ = \left[ {\matrix{
   8 &amp; { - 8}  \cr 
   { - 8} &amp; 8  \cr 

 } } \right] =  - 4\left[ {\matrix{
   { - 2} &amp; 2  \cr 
   2 &amp; { - 2}  \cr 

 } } \right] =  - 4A$$

$${A^2} = A.A = \left[ {\matrix{
